there learning English,

00:03:48.340 --> 00:03:49.930
but I feel I would come.

00:03:49.930 --> 00:03:52.670
- If every day you can make it a habit

00:03:52.670 --> 00:03:55.060
to listen to at least one motivating

00:03:55.060 --> 00:03:58.420
and inspiring learning journey story,

00:03:58.420 --> 00:04:00.860
you'll pick up on so much
knowledge and insight,

00:04:00.860 --> 00:04:02.450
and you'll feel much more confident

00:04:02.450 --> 00:04:05.400
